  {
    id: 28, category: 'National Parks & Wildlife', topic: 'Sundarbans NP',
    question: 'Which national park is famous for the Royal Bengal Tiger and mangrove forests?',
    answer: 'Sundarbans NP (West Bengal) — largest mangrove forest, UNESCO WHS, Tiger Reserve, Biosphere Reserve',
