    options: ['Bering Strait — between Russia (Siberia) and Alaska (USA); ~85 km wide; named after Vitus Bering', 'Davis Strait — between Greenland (Denmark) and Baffin Island (Canada); ~290 km wide', 'Drake Passage — between South America and Antarctica; ~800 km wide; world\'s most treacherous waters', 'Hudson Strait — between Baffin Island and Quebec (Canada); connects Hudson Bay to Atlantic Ocean'],
